Package: citihubstyle
Title: Making Ggplot Graphics In The Citihub Style
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(person("Walter", "Hjelmar", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "walter.hjelmar@citihub.com", 
    comment = "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0625-2933"))
Description: Helps create and export ggplot2 charts in the style used by 
    the Citihub data team based on the bbcplot module
